data.name: label1.ToolTip
data.value:
Value seen in Equipment Info.If using the Value from the Status screen. Trua Raw is obtained after dividing by the Weapon Class modifier.
If using the Value from the Status screen: -Remove all Skill Modifiers as they would be counted already. - In the case of Weakness Exploit or Attack Boost, just add the amount to Natural Affinity.

data.value: Uses True Raw: Level 1: +3 Attack Power Level 2: +6 Attack Power Level 3: +9 Attack Power Level 4: +12 Attack and +5% Affinity Level 5: +15 Attack and +5% Affinity Level 6: +18 Attack and +5% Affinity Level 7: +21 Attack and +5% Affinity

data.name: label9.ToolTip
data.value:
Modifier for Final Raw. 100 is full damage. 80 for Damage to Mast in Training Area. This is the percentage taken from the final raw AFTER the motion values modifiers are applied. Expect a variance of ~4% due to rounding.
Go Here for HitZone Modifiers: https://mhworld.kiranico.com/monster
